data.description: Stunning Four bedroom home in Keys Landing! This property will not disappoint, and features a spacious layout with formal living room, dining room, family room, and breakfast area! Big kitchen with lots of cabinet and counter space, as well as a butler's pantry area. One bedroom and full bathroom downstairs! Gorgeous lake views! Gated community! This one will not last!
